library(ggplot2)
library(tidyverse)

```{r}
df <- read.csv("input/processed/tt_data/rans_usda_septic.csv", stringsAsFactors = 3 TRUE)

df1 <- df %>%
  mutate(interval = df$DEPTH - df$TOP)

plot <- ggplot(df1, aes(x = log(interval))) +
  geom_histogram()

plot
```

```{r}
# top
sum(is.na(df1$TOP))
```

```{r}
# depth
sum(is.na(df1$DEPTH))
```
